sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor P as 玩家
    participant UI as UI 组件
    participant Store as gameStore(Zustand)
    participant Loop as core/gameLoop
    participant Eng as core/eventEngine
    participant FX as core/effectResolver
    participant Set as core/settlement
    participant HL as core/hiddenLines
    participant Wind as core/wind
    participant FE as core/futureEffect
    participant Mon as core/monthlyReport
    participant Sto as core/storage

    P->>UI: 打开游戏 / 刷新
    UI->>Store: loadGame()
    Store->>Sto: load('kaidian-shuo:save:v1')
    alt 无存档 或 未看教程
        UI->>P: TutorialModal（玩法说明）
        P->>UI: 我知道了 / 不再显示
        UI->>Sto: setTutorialSeen()
        UI->>P: OpeningSetup（店型/商圈/资金/装修）
        P->>Store: createNewGame(cfg)
        Store->>Sto: save()
    end

    loop 每一天（day 自增）
        Note over Loop: === 新一天开始 ===
        Loop->>FE: applyDuePendingEffects(state)
        FE-->>Loop: state'（到期 futureEffect/unlock 生效）

        Loop->>Eng: checkForcedEvents(state)
        alt cash<0 / 账单不足 / 还款>50%毛利
            Eng-->>Loop: forcedEvent (F001/F002/F003)
            Loop->>UI: CrisisModal
            P->>UI: 选续命方案
            UI->>FX: applyEffects(state, option.effects, rng)
            FX->>FX: 解析 cash 令牌 + 硬字段 + 软效果(random/futureEffect/unlock)
            FX-->>Loop: state''
        else 普通日
            Loop->>Eng: drawEvent(state, rng)
            Eng->>Eng: computeBaseProb → roll
            Eng->>Eng: selectPool(暗线权重) → 候选(trigger gate + cooldown)
            Eng-->>Loop: event | null
            opt event 存在
                Loop->>UI: EventCard / EventModal
                P->>UI: 选择选项
                UI->>FX: applyEffects(state, option.effects, rng)
                FX-->>Loop: state'' + pendingEffects
            end
        end

        UI->>P: DecisionPanel（五项决策）
        P->>UI: 调整并确认 decisions
        UI->>Loop: 携带 decisions

        Note over Loop: === 结算 ===
        Loop->>Set: resolveSettlement(state, store, decisions, mods, rng)
        Set->>Set: 基准 → 修正 → exposure → orders → revenue → 毛利 → 净利 → cash
        Set->>Set: 计算保本线 / 安全线 / 承载上限
        Set-->>Loop: DailyResult

        Loop->>HL: updateHiddenLines(state, mods)
        HL->>HL: 写 hiddenLines + decaySoftHidden
        Loop->>Wind: generateWind(state)
        Wind-->>Loop: WindMessage
        Loop->>Sto: save(state)
        UI->>P: 渲染 StatusBar/Dashboard/Log/Wind/Funnel/CashCurve

        alt day % 30 == 0（月度结算）
            Loop->>Mon: runMonthSettlement(state)
            Mon->>Mon: 汇总本月 / 债务压力 / 房租占比 / 人工占比 / 外卖占比 / 推广效率
            Mon-->>UI: MonthModal(report + 选项)
            P->>UI: 进入下月 / 优化 / 提前还贷 / 储备 / 准备分店 / 关店
            UI->>Loop: 应用月结选项（可能 openBranch）
        end

        Loop->>Loop: day += 1; 写 businessLog / eventHistory
    end

    Note over Loop,UI: 隐藏结局（任意时刻）
    Loop->>Loop: checkEndings(state)
    Loop-->>UI: EndingModal（连锁帝国/财富自由/失败/止损）
    P->>UI: 保存结局 / 继续游戏（不强制结束）
